creator: Rangam
descriptionHtml:
Connect with your community of fellow students, job seekers, and employers!

This is invitation-only app which needs the approval to join SourceAbled network
SourceAbled is designed to build a holistic workforce utilizing disability diversity and inclusion best practices. Who can use this app - university, service providers, job seeker, employers. SourceAbled is built for students and job seekers with disabilities and businesses looking to hire them. The app also offers a professionally facilitated mentorship program for skills development and day to day support.
descriptionShort: Connect with your community of fellow students, job seekers, and employers!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Performance improvement
Introduced Light and Dark theme
Performance Improvement
Accessibility Features

title: SourceAbled

creator: Rangam
descriptionHtml:
Connect with your fellow students, job seekers, and employers through the SourceAbled community platform built for untapped talent acquisition.

This is an invitation-only talent management system that supports diversity and inclusion for autism at work and neurodiversity workforce programs.

SourceAbled is designed to build a holistic workforce with unique skills utilizing disability diversity and inclusion best practices.
Universities, disability support providers, job seekers, and employers seeking autism employment solutions can use this app.
The app also offers a professionally facilitated mentorship program for skills development and day-to-day support.
descriptionShort: Connect with your fellow students, job seekers, and employers!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Thanks for using SourceAbled!
We regularly update our app to fix bugs, improve performance
Added new features for candidate and Community module
